name: io.bytes.per.checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  io.file.buffer.size.

name: mapreduce.shuffle.connection-keep-alive.timeout
description:
The number of seconds a shuffle client attempts to retain
   http connection. Refer "Keep-Alive: timeout=" header in
   Http specification

name: dfs.datanode.ec.reconstruction.stripedread.timeout.millis
description: Datanode striped read timeout in milliseconds.

name: dfs.storage.policy.satisfier.datanode.cache.refresh.interval.ms
description:
How often to refresh the datanode storages cache in milliseconds. This cache
    keeps live datanode storage reports fetched from namenode. After elapsed time,
    it will again fetch latest datanodes from namenode.
    By default, this parameter is set to 5 minutes.

name: dfs.client.socket-timeout
description: Default timeout value in milliseconds for all sockets.

name: fs.s3a.paging.maximum
description:
How many keys to request from S3 when doing
     directory listings at a time.

name: dfs.balancer.max-iteration-time
description:
Maximum amount of time while an iteration can be run by the Balancer. After
    this time the Balancer will stop the iteration, and reevaluate the work
    needs to be done to Balance the cluster. The default value is 20 minutes.
